Module kivakit.core.collections
Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.collections.primitive.map.multi

Interface PrimitiveScalarMultiMap

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    IntToByteFixedMultiMap, IntToIntFixedMultiMap, IntToLongFixedMultiMap, IntToPackedArrayFixedMultiMap, LongToByteFixedMultiMap, LongToIntFixedMultiMap, LongToIntMultiMap, LongToLongFixedMultiMap, LongToLongMultiMap
    public interface PrimitiveScalarMultiMap
    A map from one scalar primitive to another, like LongToLongFixedMultiMap or IntToByteFixedMultiMap. This interface allows all such maps to be treated the same, by widening the keys and values to long primitives.
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
    See Also:
    Quantizable
